---
title: Southern Crumbed Pork with Caramelised Veg & Kumara Wedges
description: Add sweet mustard spices to pork for a flavourful schnitzel, then serve the moreish meal with kumara wedges and caramelised broccoli and carrot. This is a dinner plate that won't be forgotten.
